T16TD4417E:350b-0: @350b `[?] // rigs gsum gyi bkra shis bzhugs /
T16TD4417E:350b-2: # // dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4417E:350b-3: yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su sku mchog ser 'dra ba //
T16TD4417E:350b-4: shes rab rtags su ral gri pu sti phyag na bsnams //
T16TD4417E:350b-5: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
T16TD4417E:350b-6: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / thugs rje'i rtags su sku mdog zla ba'i 'od chags pa //
T16TD4417E:350b-7: skyon gyis ma gos phyag mtshan phyag na padmo bsnams //
T16TD4417E:350b-8: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
T16TD4417E:350b-9: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / chos nyid mi 'gyur rtags su sku mdog mthong nag sngo //
T16TD4417E:350b-10: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med phyag na rdo rje bsnams ;
T16TD4417E:350b-11: /'phags pa phyag na rdo rje'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
T16TD4417E:350b-12: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / rigs gsum gyi bkra shis rdzogs so /
